---
title: Give Items - Street Support
description: Street support makes it easier to help homeless people. Here's how to get in touch.
layout: default.hbs
permalink: false
jsBundle: giveitems
section: givehelp
page: giveitems
---

<div class="block block--breadcrumbs">
  <div class="container">
    <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/give-help/">Give Help</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumbs__item">Give</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>
{{> no-js}}

<div class="block block--subpage-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="h1 block__header">Give</h1>
    <h2 class="h2 block__sub-header">Give items, money or time via organisations</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="block__content">
      <p>Organisations need a diverse range of resources to provide support to homeless people. If you are able to meet any of these needs, click 'I can help!' and let them know how you can support them. If you can't find any suitable needs, let us know what skills and resources you have to offer by filling in our <a href="/give-help/volunteer/">volunteer form</a>.</p>

      <div id="js-need-list-output" class="template"></div>
      {{> social-share}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<script id="js-need-list-tpl" type="text/template">
  <dl class="needs">
    \{{#needs}}
    <dt class="needs__need">
      <h3 class="h3">\{{{description}}}</h3>
      <p>\{{{reason}}}</p>
    </dt>
    <dd class="needs__more-info"><a href="\{{link}}" class="btn btn--brand-e"><span class="btn__text">I can help!</span></a></dt>
    \{{/needs}}
  </dl>
</script>

{{> loading-spinner}}
